Minecraft hosting Documentation

1. Install latest version of Java (https://www.java.com/en/download/manual.jsp)
2. Install the server files from Minecraft (https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/download/server/)
3. Launch the file to create eula, server.properties and etc files (make sure it has proper permissions (execute..etc))
4. Edit EULA file to accept terms of use
5. Launch again to open server
6. Control server through console

